- ✅ p2-maven-plugin - all compilation errors resolved
- ✅ tycho-core - all compilation errors resolved
- ✅ tycho-buildtimestamp-jgit - fixed @Inject issue
- ✅ tycho-versions-plugin - first batch fixed
- ✅ tycho-pomless - broken @Named fixed
- ✅ tycho-artifactcomparator - constants fixed

### ⚠️ Remaining Work Identified

**Known Issues:**
1. Some modules may still have broken @Named annotations with incomplete constant references
2. Other concrete classes with @Named may need interface extraction (similar to MavenDependenciesResolver)
3. At least 1 remaining @Requirement(hint=...) pattern found in codebase
4. Full 

